++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WLANalyse
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WLANalyse is a software which is looking for
WLAN accesspoints in the background. It writes
all founded accesspoints in a SQLite database
file specified in config.inc.php. The sense of
this program: After using it long time you can
generate statistics about protected and
unprotected accesspoints in your city.
PHPWLANstat is able to generate nice and graphical
HTML statistics with all the collected data.

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
REQUIREMENTS
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
- Linux/Unix
- The command "iwlist"
- WLAN
- PHP5 (minimal ubuntu-packages: php5-cli,
    php5-sqlite)
- You need to be root.

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
INSTALLATION
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
$ ./install.sh
$ mv config.inc.example.php config.inc.php

Customize the configuration file:
$ vim config.inc.php

Done!

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
USAGE
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Scanning:
$ php main.php

Generate statistic report (saved in stats/):
$ php statistics.php

